{"ID":"20230724015634-a3mzca7","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20230724015634-a3mzca7","title":"14.Docker与图形化管理工具Portainer","updated":"20230724015716"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724015636-nosdgmq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015636-nosdgmq","updated":"20230724015636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Portainer是Docker的图形化管理工具，提供状态显示面板、应用模板快速部署、容器镜像网络数据卷的基本操作（包括上传下载镜像，创建容器等操作）、事件日志显示、容器控制台操作、Swarm集群和服务等集中管理和操作、登录用户管理和控制等功能。功能十分全面，基本能满足中小型单位对容器管理的全部需求。"}]},{"ID":"20230724015636-feilqx0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015636-feilqx0","updated":"20230724015636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安装镜像"}]},{"ID":"20230724015636-mhnuyad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724015636-mhnuyad","updated":"20230724015636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"docker pull portainer/portainer"}]},{"ID":"20230724015636-i4m19od","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015636-i4m19od","updated":"20230724015636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单机方式运行"}]},{"ID":"20230724015649-cgp478w","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230724015649-cgp478w","updated":"20230724015716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2g="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"docker run -d  \\\n\n-p 9000:9000 \\   #portainer默认端口是9000，映射到本地9000端口，通过本地地址访问\n\n--restart=always \\     # 设置自动重启\n\n-v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \\     # 单机必须指定docker.sock\n\n--name partainer portainer/portainer \n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]}